title: H.S. Volleyball: Parsippany Hills’ Vikings shut out
text:
H.S. Volleyball: Parsippany Hills’ Vikings shut out October 21, 2015 Last updated: Wednesday, October 21, 2015, 12:31 AM Parsippany Life Print 
Parsippany Hills girls volleyball team were shut out by Morris Hills on Oct. 9, 2-0 in Rockaway. Here, Vikings’ Jessica Zinckgraf (18) tips the ball as Kristi Ambrosino attempts the block for Morris Hills. Parsippany Hills’ next home game will be on Friday, Oct. 30, at 5:30 p.m. against Morris Tech. © 2015 North Jersey Media Group Tags:
